body:
Verbatim back-port of #17247. The PR introduces the DeepCSV and DeepCMVA (disabled) taggers into the RECO sequences.

The PR fails at the moment due to the lack of propagation of the training files in 80X cycles. I [already contacted the admins](https://github.com/cms-data/RecoBTag-Combined/pull/4#issuecomment-281316283) to have this solved.

@slava77 , do you want me to disable the taggers and then re-inable for the legacy rereco or you prefer holding this PR until the Re-Reco release is built?
